data.description: THIS BEAUTIFUL 3 BEDROOM 2 BATH HOME IS LOCATED IN WESTLAKE ON A CANAL WITH DIRECT ACCESS TO THE WEST FORK OF THE CALCASIEU RIVER. HOME FEATURES AN OPEN FLOOR PLAN. GRANITE COUNTER TOPS IN KITCHEN AND MASTER BATHROOM. KITCHEN HAS A 4 BURNER GAS RANGE. 9-10 FOOT CEILINGS TRHOUGH OUT AS WELL AS STAINED CONCRETE FLOORS. ENJOY THE VIEW OF THE WATER FROM THE KITCHEN, LIVING ROOM AND MASTER BEDROOM.  ENJOY FAMILY TIME ON THE BACK PORCH WITH AN AMAZING VIEW OF THE WATER. MOTIVATED SELLER. THERE  IS ALSO A GENERATOR FOR THE HOME. SELLER SAYS IT NEEDS TO BE REPAIRED.
